reviewText:
When I viewed this video the first time I was amazed on what dogs can do. The video is kept short, just showing the runs of three picked trainers and their dogs which makes the video very comfortable to view. No long and tiering repeated herding over and over. But it would have been interested to see some of the other herding dogs at work (the Kelpies ore the Corgies f.e.) in comparison with the Australian Shepherd.

For the Aussie and Herding fan a must have.
